trans-unit.source: The ServiceNameElement class represents a configuration element for a service name used in a <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: De klasse ServiceNameElement vertegenwoordigt een configuratie-element voor de naam van een service gebruikt in een <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiseert een nieuw exemplaar van de <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: When this constructor is used to initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement> class, the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A> property is set to `null`.
trans-unit.target: Wanneer deze constructor is gebruikt voor het initialiseren van een nieuw exemplaar van de <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement>klasse, de <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A>eigenschap is ingesteld op `null`.</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A> </xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A> property should be set to an appropriate value for the application before calling the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection.Add%2A> method to add the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement> instance to the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: De <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A>eigenschap moet worden ingesteld op een geschikte waarde voor de toepassing voordat u de <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection.Add%2A>methode voor het toevoegen van het <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement>exemplaar van de <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection>klasse.</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection> </xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement> </xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection.Add%2A> </xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the Service Provider Name (SPN) for this <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Opgehaald of ingesteld van de Service Provider Name (SPN) voor deze <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"> </xref> exemplaar.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that contains the representation of SPN for this <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Een <xref:System.String>die bevat de weergave van de SPN voor deze <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"> </xref> exemplaar.</xref:System.String>
